The paper deals with the problem of task scheduling, which is a common topic in the field of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of state-space search algorithms and memory-limited search algorithms suggests that the paper may also belong to the categories of distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC), data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), programming languages (cs.PL), and software engineering (cs.SE).
